Package: penCalc
Version: 0.1-1
Date: 2016-06-13
Type: Package
Title: A package to calcaulate the monthly pension recieved by a person
Authors@R: c(person("Renuka", "Sane", email = "renukas@gmail.com", role = c("aut")), person("Arjun", "Gupta", email = "arjung93@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Author: Arjun Gupta [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Arjun Gupta <arjun.gupta@nipfp.org.in>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.5)
Imports: ggplot2,xtable,zoo,reshape,grid
Description: A package to calcaulate the monthly pension recieved by a person after investing a portion of his wealth into an annuity. This package will estimate the income earned by the pensionee over his lifetime by investing a portion of it into bonds, equity etc. This package will estimate the the total income and monthly income  by an individual. 
